{"tid":2055323,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【大雨警報】低壓槽相關的雷雨帶正影響本港（2020/6/8）","createTime":"2020-06-08T01:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T08:16:00.000Z","uid":38255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"667665a5083a851979861821478d516f9e27c086","tid":2055323,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T01:02:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk011\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk011&h=231cb168&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/wk012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk012&h=31a91e86&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>大雨警報：2020年6月8日</ins></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">此帖文討論期：大雨影響完結為止</span></span></strong><br />\n【註】 發出大雨警報，表示本港大部分地區可能受持續大雨影響。 此帖文為短期性質，當取消大雨警報後會隨即停用。 為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。 請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在貼文上。謝謝。 以下圖片會自動更新。<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請關注<span style=\"color: red;\">氣象巴打&bull;高登氣象台</span>最新動態<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/z4brcbr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fz4brcbr.png&h=d512611e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"http://imgur.com/2v9xh70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F2v9xh70.png&h=7ef830e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/gnzQsWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FgnzQsWS.png&h=54316817&s={SIZE}\" /></span></em><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>◤參考網頁</ins></span></span><br />\n◆ 實時天氣照片：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fts%2Findex_webcam_uc.htm&d=jILigwfP